tahli, to finish
tabli to cut in two
oktabli, to dam up OR to detour
nokshobli, to scare
shibli, to stretch
bicholli, to bend
malhalli, to scare
palhlhi, to split
polhlhi, to fold
halhlhi, to kick
lhitoffi, to unravel
kobaffi, to break in two
loffi, to peel
tokaffi, to fire a gun
